  "title": "Process Engineer (Jurong)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Define processes, system specifications, and input-output parameters to ensure hardware and software compatibility.</li>\n  <li>Conduct device qualification and application activities, developing optimized processes to meet or exceed customer requirements.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with cross-functional teams to design and implement effective process solutions.</li>\n  <li>Provide technical training and support to customers during new product or process introductions, equipment buyoff, and post-sales troubleshooting.</li>\n  <li>Assist in the development and execution of engineering plans and programs.</li>\n  <li>Perform field visits or travel as required.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor’s or Master’s degree in Engineering or Science related field</li>\n  <li>Preferable 3-5 years of process experience on high precision electro- mechanical components and system</li>\n  <li>Working experience in semi-conductor industry preferred</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd | EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R22110981| EA Personnel Name: Law Mei Fong</p>",
